title: ‘GM Street’ — The Suspension, the Trades, and the (Preseason) Games (Ep. 124)
description:
The Ringer’s Mike Lombardi and Tate Frazier discuss the suspension of Dallas Cowboys running back Ezekiel Elliott (02:00), the Buffalo Bills trading Sammy Watkins to the Los Angeles Rams (12:30), and standouts of the preseason so far (19:00).
